#. module: l10n_ve_suggested_amount
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:l10n_ve_suggested_amount.field_account_payment_register__suggested_custom_amount
msgid ""
"Suggested amount used when paying invoices involving three distinct "
"currencies. Calculates the equivalent payment amount by converting the open "
"balance from the invoice's original currency, through the company's base "
"currency, to the selected payment currency on the chosen payment date."
msgstr "Monto sugerido utilizado cuando se paga facturas que involucran tres monedas "
"Calcula el monto de pago equivalente convirtiendo el saldo abierto de la factura "
"original, a través de la moneda base de la empresa, a la moneda de pago seleccionada "
"en la fecha de pago seleccionada."
